{"tid":632263,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[求助]想搵番個90年代既機械玩具既名","createTime":"2018-04-17T08:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T08:50:02.000Z","uid":28858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fb10469260b2e94e44f5b83b01691ba2e0ce8584","tid":632263,"uid":28858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T08:28:51.000Z","msg":"想搵番個細個玩過既玩具<br />\n本身一直以為果隻野叫&ldquo;鯊魚俠&rdquo;，點知google完完全唔係果回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我印象中係一隻可以變形既機械人，深藍色<br />\n好似鯊魚又似潛艇咁樣，可以變成平時動畫見果啲機械人樣<br />\n有件武器係一個圓筒型既炮，轉動佢可以真係射到啲紅色既飛彈出黎<br />\n我諗應該有動畫既，時代大約係係90年代中-後期<br />\n有冇人知隻野叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9a01a32fd9c133d84173b2355bd92fe96decaa","tid":632263,"uid":49941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T08:33:05.000Z","msg":"黃金勇者"},{"pid":"4d8b2ab15e04e9c7bcc6fbbbc89f025a7292df39","tid":632263,"uid":26618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T08:35:05.000Z","msg":"黃金勇者既鯊魚船長／キャプテンシャーク？"},{"pid":"d404bbd397be0bc804c8c7fb9200c962dbb3da6a","tid":632263,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T08:44:46.000Z","msg":"阿童木"},{"pid":"8b109e8c301b2bbf70b7cbc7b320ceb61b978ad5","tid":632263,"uid":43530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T08:49:27.000Z","msg":"同求,細個睇左一套卡通係物件變機械人<br />\n印象中有個車轆變機械人<br />\n好似叫&quot;單高輪&quot;<br />\n求名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前有佢d玩具,搬屋掉晒,想搵返"},{"pid":"b81206ad3caecd5fef3b9cc1565bed5a4c5d1067","tid":632263,"uid":28858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df9a01a32fd9c133d84173b2355bd92fe96decaa","tid":632263,"uid":49941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T08:33:05.000Z","msg":"黃金勇者"},"citedBy"